PlantRejected(uint256).details: emitted when planting of tree with id {treeId} rejected

PlantVerified(uint256).details: emitted when planting of tree with id {treeId} verified

RegularPlantRejected(uint256).details: emitted when planting for regular tree with id {treeId} rejected

RegularPlantVerified(uint256).details: emitted when planting for regular tree with id {treeId} veirified

RegularTreePlanted(uint256).details: emitted when regular tree with id {treeId} planted

TreeAdded(uint256).details: emitted when tree with id {treeId} added

TreeAssigned(uint256).details: emitted when tree with id {treeId} assigned to planter

TreePlanted(uint256).details: emitted when tree with id {treeId} planted

TreeUpdated(uint256).details: emitted when planter send update request to tree with id {treeId}

UpdateRejected(uint256).details: emitted when update request for tree with id {treeId} rejected

UpdateVerified(uint256).details: emitted when update request for tree with id {treeId} veirified

params._treeDescription: tree description NOTE emited a {TreeAdded} event

assignTreeToPlanter(uint256,address).details: admin assign an existing tree to planter

params._planterId: assignee planter NOTE tree must be not planted NOTE emited a {TreeAssigned} event

availability(uint256,uint32).details: check if a tree is valid to take part in an auction set {_provideType} to provideStatus when tree is not in use

returns._0: 0 if a tree ready for auction and 1 if a tree is in auction or minted before

bulkRevert(uint256,uint256).details: cancel all old incremental sell of trees starting from {_startTreeId} and end at {_endTreeId}

returns._0: true in case of TreeFactory contract have been initialized

manageProvideStatus(uint256,uint256,uint.details: set incremental and communityGifts sell for trees starting from {_startTreeId} and end at {_endTreeId} by setting {_provideStatus} to provideStatus

mintRegularTrees(uint256,address).details: Transfer ownership of trees purchased by funders and Update the last tree sold This function is called only by the regularSell contract

params._lastSold: The last tree sold in the regular
params._owner: Owner of a new tree sold in Regular

returns._0: The last tree sold after update

plantTree(uint256,string,uint64,uint16).details: planter with permission to plant, can plan their tree

params._countryCode: country code of tree NOTE emited a {TreePlanted} event

regularPlantTree(string,uint64,uint16).details: This function is called by planter who have planted a new tree The planter enters the information of the new tree Information is stored in The {regularTrees} mapping And finally the tree is waiting for approval

params._countryCode: Code of the country where the tree was planted NOTE emited a {RegularTreePlanted} event

requestRegularTree(uint256,address).details: Request to buy a tree with a specific Id already planted and this function transfer ownership to funder This function is called only by the regularSell contract

params._owner: Owner of a new tree sold in Regular
params._treeId: Tree with special Id (The Id must be larger than the last tree sold)

setUpdateInterval(uint256).details: admin can set the minimum time to send next update request

returns._0: minimum time to send next update request

updateOwner(uint256,address,uint16).details: mint {_treeId} to {_ownerId} and set mintStatus to {_mintStatus} and privdeStatus to 0

updateTree(uint256,string).details: planter of  tree send update request for tree

params._treeSpecs: tree specs NOTE emited a {TreeUpdated} event

verifyPlant(uint256,bool).details: admin or allowed verifier can verify a plant or reject.

params._isVerified: true for verify and false for reject NOTE emited a {PlantVerified} or {PlantRejected} event

verifyRegularPlant(uint256,bool).details: In this function, the admin approves or rejects the pending trees After calling this function, if the tree is approved the tree information will be transferred to the {treeData}

params._isVerified: Tree approved or not NOTE emited a {RegularPlantVerified} or {RegularPlantRejected} event

verifyUpdate(uint256,bool).details: admin or allowed verifier can verifiy or reject update request for tree.

params._isVerified: true for verify and false for reject NOTE based on the current time of verifing and plant date, age of tree calculated and set as the treeStatus NOTE if a token exist for that tree (minted before) planter of tree funded based on calculated tree status NOTE emited a {UpdateVerified} or {UpdateRejected} event
params._treeId: id of tree to verify update request
